HEADWORD: Water willow
<hw>Wa"ter wil`low</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An American
aquatic plant (<spn>Dianthera Americana</spn>) with long willowlike
leaves, and spikes of small purplish flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

